latestPosts.caption:
WE DID IT!!!
New office, new energy and guess what? 
It all happened right before @socialchitchats turned 4 (shhh… technically yesterday, but who’s counting?)

I’ve dreamt of this space for sooo long — a bigger office, a bigger team and even bigger goals. We’ve worked our asses off for this moment and I’m honestly still pinching myself.

This isn’t just about a new workspace — it’s about growth, hustle, chaos and a whole lot of chai-fueled dreams coming true.

Can’t wait to show you how we’re setting this up (it’s gonna be a mess, but a fun one). 
Stay tuned — the real madness begins now!
Continue with your versions in the comments below!

latestPosts.caption:
Back in 9th grade, I started watching Roadies on MTV and instantly became a fan of @rannvijaysingha 
I looked up to him and always dreamed of meeting him one day. And now, here I am, working with him!

Over the past three years, my team and I have had the privilege of collaborating with him three times and every experience has been incredible. I still can’t believe I played table tennis with him for two hours straight! 
Every moment I’ve shared with him is special—memories I’ll cherish forever.

Rannvijay’s warmth and humility makes him truly special. He makes everyone around him feel comfortable while carrying his effortless charm.

Thank you, @rannvijaysingha for these priceless memories. 
We love you!❤️
